# Blockchain Project

## Introduction
This project demonstrates a simple blockchain smart contract.
It stores and retrieves numbers securely.

## Features
- Store a number on the blockchain
- Retrieve stored data
- Emit events when data changes

## How It Works
The smart contract is written in Solidity.
It runs on the Ethereum blockchain.

### Smart Contract Logic
The contract uses a constructor to initialize values.

## Conclusion
This project is beginner-friendly and easy to understand.
